{"data": [{"id": "4742262", "title": "Core & Main: Demand Outlook For FY25 Is Positive", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Red pipe among pink pipes\" data-id=\"2149193629\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment overview</h2> <p>I wrote about <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4661011-core-and-main-leading-player-that-is-well-positioned-to-grow\">Core &amp; Main</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CNM\" title=\"Core &amp; Main, Inc.\">CNM</a></span>) previously (January this year) with a buy rating, as I expect it to benefit greatly from the step-up in investment in US water infrastructure. I reiterate a buy</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149193629/image_2149193629.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742262-core-and-main-demand-outlook-for-fy25-is-positive", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:38:34"}, {"id": "4742260", "title": "GUT Rights Offering Results Quick Notes", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Energy saving\" data-id=\"169982512\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">deepblue4you/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>GUT's rights offering concludes</h2> <p>The rights offering for the <strong>Gabelli Utility Trust</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GUT\" title=\"Gabelli Utility Trust\">GUT</a></span>) has <a href=\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/10/22/2966967/0/en/Gabelli-Utility-Trust-Rights-Offering-Concludes-Raising-58-Million.html\" rel=\"noopener noopener noopener\">concluded</a>. We first discussed the rights offering when it was first announced in a previous <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723437-gut-2024-rights-offering-underway\">article</a>. The ex-rights</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/169982512/image_169982512.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742260-gabelli-rights-offering-results-quick-notes", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:34:05"}, {"id": "4742273", "title": "European Interest Rates: How Far To R*?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Interest rate finance and mortgage rates. Wooden block with percentage sign on many level of stack of coin. Financial growth, interest rate increase, inflation, sale price and tax rise concept.\" data-id=\"1933807369\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Wipada Wipawin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Sandra Rhouma</em></p> <p><em>When the ECB's rate-cutting cycle ends, should the neutral rate be far higher than pre-pandemic? Not in our view.</em></p> <p>With central banks worldwide now advancing through their easing cycles, investors are mulling where interest rates will</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742273-european-interest-rates-how-far-to-r", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:30:00"}, {"id": "4742259", "title": "Vinci: Why This French Company Is An A1-Sort Of Buy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Palermo, in the foreground a statue of Piazza Pretoria also known as \"Piazza della Shame\"' data-id=\"1209934581\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Angela Ravaioli/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Dear subscribers,</p> <p>In this article, I'll be looking closer once again at the French company Vinci SA (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VCISF\" title=\"Vinci SA\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:VCISF</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VCISY\" title=\"Vinci SA\">OTCPK:VCISY</a>). I firmly believe this business to be a very undervalued, underappreciated, and upside-heavy sort of business - and with a dividend yield. In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1209934581/image_1209934581.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742259-vinci-stock-this-french-company-still-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:19:40"}, {"id": "4742268", "title": "In Sickness And In Wealth: A Closer Look At Executive Pay In Healthcare", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stack of coins from low to high,tiny men on top\" data-id=\"571606663\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5184px\" height=\"3456px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Paper Boat Creative</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Bob Herr and Ryan Oden</em></p> <p>Our research suggests that healthcare firms with sound pay practices may yield healthier returns.</p> <p>In recent years, the global healthcare sector has seen rapid growth and generally strong performance. But its pay</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742268-in-sickness-and-in-wealth-a-closer-look-at-executive-pay-in-healthcare", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:15:00"}, {"id": "4742257", "title": "AT&T's Meteoric Upside Isn't Over Yet", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Smart phone with AT&amp;T.com site in the pocket\" data-id=\"458421651\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4256px\" height=\"2819px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">franckreporter</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>2024 has been a great year for shareholders of telecommunications conglomerate <strong>AT&amp;T</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/T\" title=\"AT&amp;T Inc.\">T</a></span>). Year to date, the stock is up 41.5%. And that doesn't even factor in returns from the distributions the business pays out. Since I </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742257-att-meteoric-upside-isnt-over-yet", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:05:39"}, {"id": "4742265", "title": "10 Questions For China In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Multi exposure of virtual abstract financial graph interface on Chinese flag and sunset sky background, financial and trading concept\" data-id=\"1322520591\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4500px\" height=\"3000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Igor Kutyaev</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/lynn-song/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lynn Song</a></em></p> <h2>1 - What growth target will China set for 2025?</h2> <p>China's annual exercise of setting its growth target at the Two Sessions is extremely important as it sets the tone for government policy for the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742265-10-questions-china-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:00:00"}, {"id": "4742256", "title": "Why I'm Downranking Patterson-UTI To Hold", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Drone captures a breathtaking sunset over the Permian Basin, showcasing an oil rig drilling and fracking for oil, amidst the vastness of the landscape\" data-id=\"1485934644\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">grandriver</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>After two acquisitions last year, (primarily NexTier in a 55% PTEN/45% NexTier combination, as well as technology company Ulterra), oilfield services company Patterson-UTI (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PTEN\" title=\"Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc.\">PTEN</a></span>) bit the valuation bullet in 3Q24: it took write-downs of nearly $1 billion, reducing its accounting</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742256-downranking-patterson-uti-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 11:42:41"}, {"id": "4742254", "title": "JEPQ: Dissecting Its 10% Yield", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Percentage sign\" data-id=\"1692418614\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I am not a big fan of investments that promise high yields or returns. Almost always, there is a compromise in terms of risk or a fundamental weakness. I have explored some of these weaknesses in other covered-call ETFs I recently</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742254-jepq-dissecting-its-10-percent-yield", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 11:11:00"}, {"id": "4742251", "title": "Salesforce: Defiantly An AI Play And Mr. Market Agrees", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io